conditions \n                                               (e.g., {\"NEXT_STATE\": \"If user agrees\"}). Defaults to None.\n- response_model (Optional[BaseModel]): A Pydantic model for parsing and validating the LLM's response.\n- preprocess_input (Optional[Callable]): A func to preprocess user input before sending to the LLM.\n- preprocess_chat (Optional[Callable]): A func to preprocess the chat history for the LLM.\n\nReturns:\n- callable The original function wrapped and registered with the FSM."]}, {"name": "core.fsm.LLMStateMachine.run_state_machine", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "async_openai_instance", "type": {"name": "openai.AsyncOpenAI", "xref": {"fqname": "openai.AsyncOpenAI", "project": "openai"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "user_input", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "model", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "*args", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "FSMRun", "xref": {"fqname": "core.state_models.FSMRun", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Executes a single step of the Finite State Machine (FSM) using the provided user input.\nProcesses the current state, generates a response via the LLM, and transitions the FSM.\n\nParameters:\n- async_openai_instance (openai.AsyncOpenAI): OpenAI client for API calls.\n- user_input (str): User input for the FSM.\n- model (str): The LLM model to use for generating responses (default: \"gpt-4o\").\n\nReturns:\n- FSMRun: A structured representation of the FSM's state, chat history, and response."]}, {"name": "core.fsm.LLMStateMachine.reset", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Resets